content:
Hi I finished the quiz yesterday and filled out the form but I still don't have access to the text channel. Any help is appreciated. Thanks

Ekta

Hi, Ekta! The team is adding people one by one. In the meantime, please add your state abbreviation after your name, in [brackets]. Someone may be able to help really soon, but if you don't hear anything in a couple of days, please reach out again
Is how it looks now ok? I Put FL/DC bc I stay in DC most of the year but I'm still a Florida voter
I have been trained  and did the quiz... where do we text
Hi, <@1271479084756762727> ! The team is adding people one by one. Someone may be able to help you soon, but if you don't hear anything in a couple of days, please reach out again
This is me doing that now. I did it a week ago lol

Text teams are at capacity. You'll get added when spaces open. You can also use your text team knowledge with other text banking campaigns like https://events.democrats.org/event/433467/, you can "text" in the filter on the https://events.democrats.org/ page.

<@1271479084756762727> While we appreciate you are interested in text, the phone banking is actually much more effective all around. We have great support for new phone bankers, you will be embraced by wonderful group experience and even if you don't manage to talk to anyone on the phone, you being there will push the numbers up which makes the dialer move faster and others on your team will be able to connect with more folks.
Hi I clinked mobile inbox. I didn’t see #Noaccess. How do we know if we are adding to the text team? Thanks
Mobile inbox is different then text team.
